    <svcsubproc>
        <title>Wheelchair Seat Belts and Shoulder Harness</title>
        <para>The wheelchair seat belts and shoulder harness assemblies are attached to the floor and wall harness track
            assemblies. When not in use the harness and seat belt assemblies may be stored in a shoulder harness storage
            bag (
            <hotlnk document="s47005_27.xml" xrefid="f4700579">Fig. 79, Item 2</hotlnk>).
        </para>
        <step1>
            <para count="1">To remove the shoulder harness assembly track, locate the track section (
                <hotlnk document="s47005_27.xml" xrefid="f4700578">Fig. 78, Item 2</hotlnk>) above the bus body light
                bar along the upper section of the body (if equipped).
            </para>
        </step1>
        <step1>
            <para count="1">Locate the torque head mounting screws (
                <hotlnk document="s47005_27.xml" xrefid="f4700578">Fig. 78, Item 3</hotlnk>). Loosen and remove.
            </para>
        </step1>
        <step1>
            <para count="1">Remove the harness track assembly.</para>
        </step1>
    </svcsubproc>
